{"tid":283840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱入𨋢有隻曱甴","createTime":"2017-06-14T12:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T16:20:27.000Z","uid":42212,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"360d0f0cfa3dd66adeb9d4311232ad0d80f4a31b","tid":283840,"uid":42212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:57:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的，本身前面個女人入緊𨋢，但係一行入去即刻跳出來，原來架𨋢有隻細曱甴，咁𨋢入邊呢已經有對父子嘅，個肥仔應該小五小六既，我唔理啦就入𨋢就踩死隻曱甴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個老豆就問個肥仔：你驚啊唔敢踩啊？<br />\n<br />\n肥仔就答：係啊<br />\n<br />\n咁個老豆笑個肥仔：乜咁細膽㗎唔夠膽踩男人老狗<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候呢肥仔好快覆咗句<br />\n<br />\n「咁你又唔踩」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我忍笑忍到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要同我住同一層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d7cdbedc85ce64ab3da0571efc70c5c7a32d69","tid":283840,"uid":36981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4f277817d5a182f93ed03c61d73c4423764567","tid":283840,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea6d6ab4fb98bd318cd91c6b0b004a56e905f55","tid":283840,"uid":108885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\